f=Engineering/quinn/custom/test-strategy/assets/stack-notes-rust-testing-2026-07.md · h1:Stack Notes Rust Testing (dated 2026-07)=**Applies business's stack-profile names Rust.** Method authority: `test-strategy` (tiers, floors, gate conflicts resolve there). Source: affaan-m/everything-claude-code `rust-testing`, adopted 2026-07-10, condensed. Verify tool versions months old. · h2:TDD cycle=RED (test first, `todo!()` placeholder) GREEN (minimal pass) REFACTOR (tests stay green). Matches Shared red-green regression rule. · te:tiers Rust mechanics (test-strategy's pyramid mapped)=**Unit:** `#[cfg(test)] mod tests` in-module; `assert_eq!` over `assert!` (better failures); float compares `EPSILON`., **Integration:** `tests/` dir file binary; shared utilities `tests/common/mod.rs`., **Doc tests:** examples `///` docs executable API docs can't rot; `no_run` network/setup-dependent examples., **Property-based:** `proptest` invariants (roundtrips, length-preservation, ordering) custom strategies domain values (e.g. valid-email generator)., **Parameterized:** `rstest` cases fixtures., **Async:** `#[tokio::test]`; timeouts `tokio::time::timeout`; **never `sleep()`** channels/barriers/`tokio::time::pause()`. · h2:Error/panic testing=Prefer asserting `Result::is_err()` `matches!(err, Variant(_))` over `#[should_panic]`; tests returning `Result` use `?` clean failures. · h2:Mocking=`mockall` `#[automock]` traits; expectations `.with(eq(..))`, `.times(n)`, `.returning(..)`. Don't mock everything prefer integration tests feasible. · h2:Coverage (feeds test-strategy's operator-set floors)=`cargo llvm-cov` (`--html`, `--lcov`, `--fail-under-lines 80`). Source targets: critical logic 100% public API 90%+ general 80%+ generated/FFI excluded. **Actual floors operator-set quinn-config source's defaults, VYON law.** · h2:Commands=`cargo test` `-- --nocapture` `--lib` `--test <name>` `--doc` `--no-fail-fast` `-- --ignored`. Benchmarks: criterion (`harness false`, `black_box`). · h2:CI shape=fmt --check clippy `-D warnings` test llvm-cov floor. Pipeline itself ops's domain; gate verdict stays quinn's. · h2:Flaky tests=Fix quarantine never ignore (test-strategy's quarantined-and-counted rule applies unchanged).